Package: affiner
Type: Package
Title: A finer way to render 3D objects in 'grid' using affine transformations
Version: 0.1.0-2
Authors@R: c(person("Trevor L", "Davis", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "trevor.l.davis@gmail.com",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6341-4639")))
Description: Translate, rotate, dilate, and project 2D and 3D points.  Use the 'grid's "affine transformation" feature to render textured flat surfaces.
